---
title: Plant-Based Mince, Spinach & Ricotta Ravioli with Garlicky Tomato Sauce & Parmesan
description: Pillowy spinach and ricotta ravioli take a dip in a rich tomato ragu, soaking up all that saucy goodness. A sprinkle of Parmesan on top? Chef’s kiss! This comforting, flavour-packed dish is like a warm hug for your taste buds.

